description: The iBoxx Euro Germany Total Return Index aims to reflect the performance of the following market: EUR-denominated bonds issued by the German government Exposure across the whole yield curve (minimum time to maturity of 1 year) Minimum amount outstanding of EUR 1 billion per bond Additional information on the Index and the general methodology behind the Markit iBoxx indices can be found on Markit iBoxx website ( https://www.markit.com ).
name: Xtrackers II Germany Government Bond UCITS ETF 1C
